{"tid":613914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙煞持刀兇司機 深水埗搶Skyline","createTime":"2018-04-02T05:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T06:46:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a59a86d177129022f8993b2b524c30c46a1795","tid":613914,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180402/20350145\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F20350145&d=qVPnPxya8ceNoUVqXCKWBP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f68f809b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F20350145&h=c05789a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180402/20350145</a><br />\n<br />\n雙煞持刀兇司機<br />\n深水埗搶Skyline<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n【本報訊】深水埗昨凌晨發生搶車案，賊人在街頭持刀指嚇一名駕駛日產Skyline跑車的男子，逼令他落車後將車劫走。警方接報在附近兜截無果，現正追查歹徒犯案動機及緝捕兩賊歸案。<br />\n<br />\n被搶走的日產Skyline跑車，2003年出廠，2006年首次登記，女車主姓張，報住天水圍天逸邨，當年她以約19萬元購入該車。被搶車男子姓黃(42歲)，事後隨警員返警署協助調查，他聲稱不認識兩名搶車賊，車上亦無值錢財物，自己亦無結怨及欠債，不知為何被搶車。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨日凌晨零時許，黃駕駛Skyline跑車沿深水埗大南街行駛至黃竹街交界讓線位停下時，兩名男子突然趨前拉開其車門，其中一人用刀指嚇黃逼令他下車，黃在刀尖指嚇下只好就範，其後兩賊人登車將車開走，逃去無蹤。黃事後報警，警方接報在附近兜截，但並無發現。警方調查後將案件列擅自取去交通工具及藏有攻擊性武器，由深水埗警區刑事調查隊跟進。"},{"pid":"ad6c68979f4998eb0ce4492273219c40f1133f29","tid":613914,"uid":80966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2548c77f167decdcbece692f91bceba7fb13bd66","tid":613914,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:46:46.000Z","msg":"GTA"},{"pid":"25ceb01a22b16ec2435153d118a1df39fcb2338f","tid":613914,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"Skyline GTR?"},{"pid":"e4ef85f830693cf6c2043d24447e4cfc77d0a138","tid":613914,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:25:26.000Z","msg":"惡撚到，拍得住美國黑鬼，但你伸枝槍出黎就會散退"},{"pid":"4775501ebf51f8be8830f59664b5c39b31ca6cee","tid":613914,"uid":71100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"車上有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a583b14a3f07f9723ad7a8ea8ac320c85e6308","tid":613914,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad6c68979f4998eb0ce4492273219c40f1133f29","tid":613914,"uid":80966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"好似GTA咁<br />\n隨便一部車都可以打開車門立即搶走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffd001dba5cc623ac859c6ec1315e067ec318d2","tid":613914,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"喺架車入面做咩要自己落車？"},{"pid":"d4837adf7a7fbbf85baa2180f7362b6dce7ad934","tid":613914,"uid":165360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}